OL,3,CFootball fan who died after pub crash
OL,4,Cmade 'worst decision of his life'
OL,6,FThe mum of a "loving and kind"
OL,7,Ffootball fan who died in a car crash
OL,8,Fafter celebrating England's Euro 2024
OL,9,Fwin over Slovakia, said he made the
OL,10,F"worst decision of his life".
OL,12,FWill Place, 23, who had only recently
OL,13,Fgraduated from university, died after
OL,14,Fhis car smashed into the White Lion
OL,15,Fpub in Heywood, Greater Manchester,
OL,16,Fand erupted into flames.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
