OL,3,CFootball fan who died after pub crash
OL,4,Cmade 'worst decision of his life'
OL,6,FThe crash happened after police
OL,7,Fofficers in a patrol car had attempted
OL,8,Fto stop the vehicle on nearby Bolton
OL,9,FRoad moments before, at around 3:15am
OL,10,Fon 1 July
OL,12,FHis mum Beverley Place, a Labour
OL,13,Fcouncillor and a former mayor of
OL,14,FRochdale, has since issued a tribute
OL,15,Fto her son saying he made "the worst
OL,16,Fdecision of his life" celebrating
OL,17,FEngland's 2-1 extra-time win against
OL,18,FSlovakia in the Round of 16, and "paid
OL,19,Fthe ultimate price".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
