OL,3,CFootball fan who died after pub crash
OL,4,Cmade 'worst decision of his life'
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,7,Fofficers engaged in a "short pursuit"
OL,8,Fwith Mr Place's Dacia Sandero onto
OL,9,FRochdale Road East, which was stopped
OL,10,Fa short time later.
OL,12,FGMP said the incident had been
OL,13,Freferred to the Independent Office for
OL,14,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) in line with
OL,15,Fnormal procedure.
OL,17,FIn a statement, Cllr Place said: "Will
OL,18,Fwas adored by all that knew him. He
OL,19,Fwas a special person, with a heart of
OL,20,Fgold, who lit up every room with his
OL,21,Finfectious smile and personality.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
