OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F393A1720093125
OL,3,CFootball fan who died after pub crash
OL,4,Cmade 'worst decision of his life'
OL,6,F"He was passionate about football and
OL,7,Fin the early hours of Monday morning,
OL,8,Fafter celebrating the England team's
OL,9,Fwin, Will acted completely out of
OL,10,Fcharacter and made the worst decision
OL,11,Fof his life and tragically paid the
OL,12,Fultimate price.
OL,14,F"We are all left utterly bereft and
OL,15,Fheartbroken. We are grateful for the
OL,16,Foutpouring of grief, love and support
OL,17,Fwe have received from his innumerable
OL,18,Ffriends."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
