OL,4,Cmade 'worst decision of his life'
OL,6,FMr Place, who graduated with a BA
OL,7,FHonours degree in multimedia sports
OL,8,Fjournalism in January and was also a
OL,9,Fbudding farmer, wrote match reports at
OL,10,Fnon-league side Ramsbottom United and
OL,11,Fworked at Roch Valley Radio in
OL,12,FRochdale.
OL,14,FPaying tribute, his girlfriend Megan
OL,15,FWild said: "I feel like someone has
OL,16,Ftaken my heart out of my body. We have
OL,17,Fspent everyday together for nearly
OL,18,Feight years and now there's nothing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
