OL,3,CFootball fan who died after pub crash
OL,4,Cmade 'worst decision of his life'
OL,6,F"He was the kindest, most loving
OL,7,Fperson, even when he was having a bad
OL,8,Fday. He will do anything to help
OL,9,Fanyone. Nothing can replace him in
OL,10,Fthis world and now I'm just left
OL,11,Fempty."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the IOPC said:
OL,14,F"Following a referral from Greater
OL,15,FManchester Police, we have started an
OL,16,Findependent investigation into the
OL,17,Fcircumstances of a fatal collision on
OL,18,FYork Street in Heywood.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
