OL,3,CFootball fan who died after pub crash
OL,4,Cmade 'worst decision of his life'
OL,6,F"We were notified by the force that a
OL,7,Fcar had collided into the White Lion
OL,8,Fpub at 3:15am on 1 July after
OL,9,Freportedly failing to stop for police
OL,10,Fofficers minutes before the incident.
OL,11,FSadly, the male driver of the vehicle
OL,12,Fdied at the scene.
OL,14,F"We sent investigators to the scene,
OL,15,Fas well as to the police post-incident
OL,16,Fprocedures, to begin gathering
OL,17,Fevidence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
