OL,6,F"An independent investigation was
OL,7,Fdeclared shortly before 5am. Our
OL,8,Fthoughts are with all of those
OL,9,Faffected by this tragic incident. Our
OL,10,Finvestigation is in its very early
OL,11,Fstages."
